Items.mt: Only after Luo Yan Valley changed ownership, the word on the street was that there were treasures at the bottom of the valley, and the secret manual seemed to have never existed.

Items.r: 只不过洛雁谷易主后，坊间消息就成了谷底有宝物，秘笈一事彷佛没存在过。
